{{wikipedia}}
==English==
===Pronunciation===
*(''US''): [[IPA]]: /ˌpæ.nəˈɹæ.mə/

===Etymology===
From the Greek ''παν'' (''pan'' - ''all''), + ''όραμα'' (''horāma'' - ''sight'').

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# an [[unbroken]] [[view]] of an [[entire]] [[surround]]ing [[area]]
# a [[picture]] or [[series]] of pictures representing a [[continuous]] [[scene]]
#(''figurative'') a [[comprehensive]] [[survey]]

